data.description: Don't miss this charming little doll house in an established neighborhood! Oversized covered front porch is perfect for morning coffee. New front and rear doors. New paint throughout entire home 2023. Ceramic tile w/ the wood floor look throughout the main living areas! New flooring in all 3 bedrooms. The living room features a woodburning fireplace and custom painted accent wall. Cute kitchen with updates and a breakfast room with backyard access. Nice sized master bedroom with newly remodeled walk-shower private bathroom. Bedrooms 2 and 3 share a hall bath. Backyard is board on board privacy fenced, built in 2018, with storm cellar. New roof was installed in 2020. This one won't last long!
